des:
Are you the one who needs somebody to push you when it comes to health and fitness?

Well Alexa has just got smarter!
With the Fitness Facts skill, Alexa will keep you motivated, by telling some really interesting facts about your body and living healthy, so enable the skill and ask, "Alexa, tell me a fitness fact?!"

Note: The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
